<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.9.11">
<l>tiruvaṭiyai nāraṇaṉaikkēcavaṉaip parañcuṭarait</l>
<l>tiruvaṭicēr vatukarutic ceḻuṅkurukūrc caṭakōpaṉ</l>
<l>ṟiruvaṭimē luraittatami ḻāyirattu ḷippattun</l>
<l>tiruvaṭiyē yaṭaivikkun tiruvaṭicērn toṉṟumiṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>These ten among the Tamil thousand spoken at the holy feet</l>
<l>by Caṭakōpaṉ from ample Kurukūr, in the intent of joining the holy feet,</l>
<l>on the holy feet, on Nāraṇaṉ, Kēcavaṉ, the highest light,</l>
<l>will make one attain the holy feet. As one join the holy feet.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
